<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>html12.png</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg1:#0f172a; --bg2:#1e293b; --accent:#ff6a2b; --muted:#cbd5e1;
    }
    *{box-sizing:border-box} html,body{height:100%}
    body{
      margin:0; display:grid; place-items:center; min-height:100%;
      background: radial-gradient(1200px 600px at 20% 20%, #1f2a44 0%, #0b1324 45%, #071022 100%);
      font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
      color:#e6edf6;
    }
    .card{
      width: 760px; padding: 42px; border-radius: 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg2), var(--bg1));
      box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.35), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.06);
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .ring{
      position:absolute; width:520px; height:520px; border-radius:50%;
      right:-140px; top:-140px; filter: blur(10px);
      background:
        conic-gradient(from 120deg at 50% 50%, rgba(255,255,255,.06), rgba(255,106,43,.25), rgba(255,255,255,.06));
      opacity:.6;
    }
    h1{margin:0 0 10px; font-size:38px; letter-spacing:.3px}
    p{margin:0 0 18px; color:var(--muted); font-size:18px}
    .row{display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap}
    .tag{
      padding:8px 12px; border-radius:999px; font-weight:700; font-size:13px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.06); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    }
    .cta{
      margin-top:22px;
      display:inline-block; padding:12px 16px; border-radius:12px;
      background:var(--accent); color:#fff; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:.2px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(255,106,43,.35);
    }
    .badge{
      position:absolute; left:22px; top:22px; font-weight:800;
      padding:6px 10px; border-radius:10px; background:rgba(255,255,255,.08); font-size:12px
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="badge">Version 12</div>
    <div class="ring" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <h1>Demo 12 â€” HTML Preview</h1>
    <p>Clean hero card to export as <strong>html12.png</strong>. Subtle gradients, glassy ring and crisp CTA.</p>
    <div class="row" style="margin-bottom:10px">
      <span class="tag">responsive</span>
      <span class="tag">landing</span>
      <span class="tag">minimal</span>
    </div>
    <a class="cta" href="#" onclick="return false">Get Started</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
